// Plinko paytables + geometry helpers.
//
// PLINKO_TABLES is generated by scripts/gen_plinko.mjs and is the SAME data
// embedded in supabase/migrations/0014_plinko.sql. The server is authoritative
// for the payout; the client uses these only to draw the bucket labels and to
// size the board. If you change one, regenerate and update BOTH.

